---
import {
  getGoogleOAuthRedirectUri,
  getGoogleOAuthSenderAddress,
} from '@/lib/googleOAuth'

export const prerender = false

const redirectUri = getGoogleOAuthRedirectUri()
const graduationAddress = getGoogleOAuthSenderAddress('graduacao')
const postAddress = getGoogleOAuthSenderAddress('posgraduacao')
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <title>Google OAuth - Faculdade de Psicologia</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
      }

      body {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0b1730 0%, #073a35 100%);
        color: #f7f8fb;
        font-family: "Kumbh Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      main {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 880px;
        padding: 48px 24px 80px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin: 0 0 12px;
      }

      p,
      li {
        color: rgba(247, 248, 251, 0.88);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        color: #101828;
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 16px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .item {
        border: 1px solid rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.12);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .item strong,
      code {
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .button {
        align-items: center;
        background: #0b6b61;
        border-radius: 12px;
        color: #fff;
        display: inline-flex;
        font-weight: 700;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 16px;
        min-height: 48px;
        padding: 0 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 16px 0 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Google OAuth 2.0</h1>
      <p>Use esta pagina para gerar os refresh tokens das duas caixas Gmail.</p>

      <div class="card">
        <strong>Redirect URI configurada:</strong>
        <p><code>{redirectUri}</code></p>

        <div class="grid">
          <section class="item">
            <strong>Graduacao</strong>
            <p><code>{graduationAddress}</code></p>
            <a class="button" href="/api/google-oauth/start?mailbox=graduacao">
              Autorizar graduacao
            </a>
          </section>

          <section class="item">
            <strong>Pos-graduacao</strong>
            <p><code>{postAddress}</code></p>
            <a class="button" href="/api/google-oauth/start?mailbox=posgraduacao">
              Autorizar pos-graduacao
            </a>
          </section>
        </div>

        <ul>
          <li>Ao finalizar, o callback vai mostrar o refresh token e o nome da variavel de ambiente.</li>
          <li>Use uma conta por vez, logada na caixa correta do Google Workspace.</li>
          <li>Depois que os tokens forem gerados, nao deixe esta pagina publica por mais tempo que o necessario.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
